est Mobile App Development Framework 2022<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/open-source-technology-trends.html\/#Open_Source_Technology_%E2%80%93_The_Way_Forward_for_CMS_Development\" title=\"Open Source Technology \u2013 The Way Forward for CMS Development\">Open Source Technology \u2013 The Way Forward for CMS Development<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/open-source-technology-trends.html\/#Best_Open_Source_CMS_Platforms_in_2022\" title=\"Best Open Source CMS Platforms in 2022\">Best Open Source CMS Platforms in 2022<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/open-source-technology-trends.html\/#Open_Source_Promote_RESTful_API-Based_Development\" title=\"Open Source Promote RESTful API-Based Development\">Open Source Promote RESTful API-Based Development<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/open-source-technology-trends.html\/#Open_Source_is_everywhere%E2%80%A6\" title=\"Open Source is everywhere\u2026\">Open Source is everywhere\u2026<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Open Source Technology Trends 2022 will play a pivotal role in modern computing, particularly in application development and IT infrastructure. With open source\u2019s rapid rise in prominence, the trends remain relatively obscure to the world. Open Source being the ground zero for technology development definitely has become the preferred way of growing hot new technology, [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":9794,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","forma